Text: Anyone got this to work on win7 yet?
Everything went smooth on VISTA. Good Keygen. Thanks to the UPLOADER and seeders you are greatly appreciated.

On the setup:
1. Right click 
2. Go to properties
3. Go to compatibility tab
4. Check the box that says, "Run this program in compatibility mode for:"
5. Make sure the drop down box is on, "Windows XP (Service Pack 3)"
6. Apply then OK

If that doesn't work install it regularly and do the above steps on the program itself.
